A Monokai-based color scheme for IntelliJ IDEA 12 and primarily Scala (plus other goodies like JavaScript, Java, etc.).

For OS X Mountain Lion,
Place the .xml in ~/Library/Preferences/{IntelliJIdea12, IdeaIC12}/colors/ and restart IDEA.

For Windows,
Place the .xml in %HOMEPATH%.IntelliJIdea12\config\colors and restart IDEA.

Based off of http://tumblr.teamon.eu/post/697864114/intellij-idea-monokai-color-theme and https://github.com/tomasr/molokai, colorization may change by my whim.

